---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Ahmed Omrane — CTO-level operator specializing in constraint-to-scale engineering.">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="page-inner">
      <header class="page-header">
        <p class="label">About</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Ahmed Omrane</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="bio">
        <p>
          I build and govern technical systems at the intersection of constraint and scale — the place where engineering decisions have direct P&amp;L consequences and where the wrong move compounds for years. My background is in CTO-level operator work across early-stage and growth-phase companies: building engineering organisations from scratch, navigating founder-driven environments, and transitioning live platforms without downtime.
        </p>
        <p>
          My practice is constraint-to-scale engineering: establishing governance-fit systems under resource, organisational, and technical constraints. This means sequencing correctly before building, treating architecture as a business decision, and designing for the system to run without me. The case files and playbooks on this site document how that looks in practice.
        </p>
        <p>
          I use AI systems architecturally, not as acceleration tools — as a second cognitive layer with explicit governance, a structured retrieval corpus, and strict separation between long-term knowledge and live context. This shapes how I think about both my own leverage and the systems I build for teams.
        </p>
        <p>
          Based in France, with a European market focus and an international operating background.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact">
        <p class="label">Contact</p>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/omrane-ahmed/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .page-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-content);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--size-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    display: block;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--size-2xl);
  }

  .bio {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .bio p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--size-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact {
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .contact-links a:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-inner {
      padding: 0 var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
